<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <h1>New Timeslot</h1>
    <p>
    Make a regular "timeslot" that you'll be available for a weekly conversation. If
    your followers are interested, they will sign up for the timeslot, and it
    will create a live conversation event on the site's main calendar.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <%= render 'form', timeslot: @timeslot %>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <%= link_to 'Back', timeslots_path %>
  </div>
</div>
